query:
SELECT i.id, i.status, i.errorMessage, i.beforeScreenshotUrl, i.afterScreenshotUrl, i.executedAt, i.createdAt 
FROM interactions i 
WHERE i.interactionType = 'like' 
ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 3
